{"tid":1564526,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過，簡體字將會成為國際認可嘅魔鬼符號？","createTime":"2019-09-12T21:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T21:39:47.000Z","uid":271601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dd552d518e45484e3e4ae5aca2cc79bead773686","tid":1564526,"uid":271601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T21:31:37.000Z","msg":"用字體代表國家，之前納粹德國就試過，就係呢隻統稱為 Blackletter 嘅字體：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.wired.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/118lAC1hbd9EPmya4VvQ14Q-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F118lAC1hbd9EPmya4VvQ14Q-1.png&h=785dc7ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n納粹敗走之後，Blackletter 成為禁忌。<br />\n／Why don&rsquo;t we use blackletter anymore? The answer is literally &ldquo;Hitler.&rdquo; Nazi leadership used Fraktur, an archetypal variety of blackletter, as their official typeface. They positioned it as a symbol of German national identity and denounced papers that printed with anything else.／<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wired.com/2017/05/how-fonts-are-fueling-the-culture-wars\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2F2017%2F05%2Fhow-fonts-are-fueling-the-culture-wars&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmPLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=d945031f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wired.com/2017/05/how-fonts-are-fueling-the-culture-wars</a><br />\n<br />\n當然，有藝術意義嘅，仍然會沿用，譬如想突顯自己係衰人：<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.wired.com/photos/59421ee60221283cb54e74f8/master/w_532,c_limit/1XSO25q3hmVLLuvPSw1osog-1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.wired.com%2Fphotos%2F59421ee60221283cb54e74f8%2Fmaster%2Fw_532%2Cc_limit%2F1XSO25q3hmVLLuvPSw1osog-1.jpeg&h=a3140139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">A tattoo identifying a member of the MS-13 gang.</span><br />\n<br />\n講返中国，其實反環球化一早出現，貿易戰只係果，唔係因：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ecri-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/downloads/150130_Twitter_W495.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fecri-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fdownloads%2F150130_Twitter_W495.gif&h=0de98d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n／其實有冇 Trump 呢個傻佬搞貿易戰，環球化點睇都係尾聲。Business Cycle 係睇長線經濟嘅研究社，佢哋 2015 就提過環球出口增長，今個十年同上一個十年相比係跌咗一級（圖 1）。<br />\n<br />\n幅圖係舊啲，不過到 2017 update，佢哋仍然發覺情況無變，環球增長縱有改善，但跳唔出 5% upper limit 嘅 range，同金融海嘯前嘅 10% 相比，仍然係跌咗一級／<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/subnet142/posts/10156417065249905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsubnet142%2Fposts%2F10156417065249905&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmPLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=cd8c93e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/subnet142/posts/10156417065249905</a><br />\n<br />\n中国勃起係靠環球化，反環球化就會陽痿，所以2008用4萬億谷經濟，結果只係谷起地產，其他毫無寸進，因為反環球化抵銷咗個推動力。依家中国成日講要資金流入實體經濟，就係呢個原因，因為現時「繁榮」只係高樓價，並唔係高生產力。中国向香港學習，好學唔學，學咗最敗家嗰招。<br />\n<br />\n貿易戰係果，而事情往往發展到呢個階段，隨後就係環球經濟衰退。上次2008，中国仍然未踏入人口老化階段，而當時西方亦未對中国有敵意，大家合作，中国並無大礙。不過今次就會好唔同，中国會大傷，好大機會四分五裂，如果中途發動戰爭分散國內注意力嘅話，中国將會被永久解體。<br />\n<br />\n真係有咁嘅一日，新疆西藏呢啲從來都唔係中國人嘅中国人，佢哋當然會恢復用自己文字，但漢族就要揀用邊一種漢字字體喇。一定會出現一部份係親西方，另一部份係繼續列寧主義嘅。簡體字仍然會存在，不過就係代表列寧同盟。唔想同流合污嘅，自然要取締簡體字。"},{"pid":"86756459d68e0651b26dbb741a8f966ed4384db9","tid":1564526,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T21:32:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"171000579ea0fb7aa5389a258f7893446d22da30","tid":1564526,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T21:33:44.000Z","msg":"希望你可以幫我share呢篇文, 我知呢篇文好長, 如果唔想睇曬既話入黎睇下堆subheading都好, 我好有信心呢篇文係可以幫助打破現況 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"db7f124c63c1fdc70062c06dfea31c0b1d2d3e30","tid":1564526,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T21:39:47.000Z","msg":"咁繁體字就係antifraktur<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}